@function hx.icon
  @deprecated 2.0.0
    @description
      Replaced by @code[hx.i]

  @added 1.0.0
    @description
      Fluid api for constructing icons

  @description
    Creates a detached @code[<i>] element wrapped in a selection

  @arg? options [Object]
    @property class [String]
      @description
        The class to apply to the icon. This assumes you are using an icon font that uses classes (for example, font awsome)

  @returns [Selection]
    @description
      The selection containing the new element

